<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>A dragon makes=
 its
lair an extension of itself, and can use Lair Sense to notice intruders
anywhere within its lair. Whenever a character makes a test within the conf=
ines
