<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>This gruesome
ability allows the Horror to mutilate a target’s body. The Horror touches=
 the
target and makes a Spellcasting Test against the target’s Spell Defense. =
If the
test succeeds, the Horror rolls the Skin Shift dice to determine damage. The
target takes Damage Points equal to the result of the Skin Shift dice roll;=
 his
skin tears loose from muscles and ligaments, twisting and rotating about his
