<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Action: Standa=
rd</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Type: Mundane<=
/p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>This power all=
ows a
creature to shatter brittle objects—including crystal armor and weapons,
glassware, pottery, and so on. The creature makes a Sonic Shriek Test and
compares the result against the Spell Defense (increased by +10) of each it=
em
within range. If the test succeeds, the object shatters into hundreds of
pieces. Weapons and armor crack horribly or break into fragments; potion
bottles crack and spill their contents to the ground.</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Magical items
(including magically-enhanced crystal armor and weapons) are almost immune =
to
the effects of a Sonic Shriek attack; they only shatter on an Extraordinary
result. The power’s range is listed with the creature’s description.</p>

