<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:17.0pt'>Spear</p>

</div>

<div style=3D'direction:ltr;margin-top:.4506in;margin-left:0in;width:7.6041=
in'>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Step: STR + St=
rength
